      <section eId="sec_15_4_6">
        <num>15-4-6</num>
        <content>
          <p>The Supreme Court and the Court of Appeals shall employ and fix the salaries of such stenographers, clerical assistants, and employees as are necessary for the performance of the duties in the offices of the reporter and assistant reporter of decisions of such courts. The salaries of such employees shall be paid by the clerks of the respective courts, one-half each by each court from the appropriations for the operation of the respective courts.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1943, p. 387, ยง 9.)</p>
